description:
Spin-off from Crikey! focusing on fictional spies in the movies, tv and comics.

Issue one includes:

  • The Prisoner
  • Avengers - Emma Peel
  • Nick Fury Agent of SHIELD
  • Stingray - Troy Tempest
  • The Man from UNCLE
  • James Bond - George Lazenby
  • The Champions
  • Brent Cleever - Secret Agent 21 (TV21 comic)
